.TH "cmp_connection_init" 9 "cmp_connection_init" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
cmp_connection_init \- initializes a connection manager
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" cmp_connection_init
.BI "(struct cmp_connection *c "  ","
.BI "struct fw_unit *unit "  ","
.BI "enum cmp_direction direction "  ","
.BI "unsigned int pcr_index "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "c" 12
the connection manager to initialize
.IP "unit" 12
a unit of the target device
.IP "direction" 12
input or output
.IP "pcr_index" 12
the index of the iPCR/oPCR on the target device
